Title: Not Yet Lost
Description:
The flame did not take root here on a whim. 

No doubt there are servants of the Firelands cloistered within, trying to spread their flame to the creatures that reside within these barrows. We must do what we can to save those who can still be saved, and mete out swift justice to the heretics that lurk within.
ObjectivesText: Rescue the denizens of the Sor'theril Barrow Den.
